    "body": "[ LP comment 1 by: Fernando Perez, on 2009-04-01 08:54:29.508660+00:00 ]\n\nThis would be very useful, as long as we restrict it to only cases when you are editing history input lines.  We don't want the case\n\n%edit filename.py\n\nto dump the entire contents of filename.py into the history!\n\nBut for input lines it does seem like a better implementation than what we have right now.\n"
